                <div class="project-card">
                    <div class="project-header">
                        <h3>GraphEm</h3>
                        <div class="project-links">
                            <a href="https://igorrivin.github.io/graphem-site/" target="_blank" class="project-link">Project Site</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="project-description">
                        Comprehensive graph embedding software that maps complex network structures into low-dimensional spaces 
